---
import StudioPageNav from "./StudioPageNav";
import type { Locale } from "../lib/site-locale";

const { locale = "es" } = Astro.props as { locale?: Locale };

const content = {
  es: {
    heroLabel: "QUIÉNES SOMOS",
    heroTitle: "Recuperamos oportunidades que tu negocio pierde cada día",
    heroBody:
      "Ayudamos a restaurantes y pequeñas empresas a no perder reservas, ventas o conversaciones valiosas cuando no pueden contestar a tiempo.",
    heroStats: [
      { value: "24/7", label: "Respuesta automática" },
      { value: "1 contacto", label: "1 oportunidad recuperable" },
      { value: "0 excusas", label: "Para perder una venta" },
    ],
    introLabel: "EL PROBLEMA",
    introTitle: "Lo que pasa todos los días y casi nadie mide",
    introParagraphs: [
      "En muchos negocios, especialmente restaurantes y pequeñas empresas, hay algo que pasa todos los días y casi nadie se da cuenta de cuánto dinero cuesta: llamadas que no se pueden atender, mensajes que quedan sin responder y clientes que terminan reservando o comprando en otro sitio.",
      "La mayoría de los dueños están ocupados gestionando el negocio, atendiendo clientes, coordinando al equipo y resolviendo problemas del día a día. El seguimiento de llamadas o de contactos muchas veces queda en segundo plano, y ahí es donde se pierden oportunidades reales de venta.",
    ],
    painPoints: [
      {
        title: "Llamadas perdidas",
        body: "Cuando no puedes coger el teléfono, muchas veces el cliente no vuelve a intentarlo.",
      },
      {
        title: "Mensajes sin respuesta",
        body: "Cada consulta no atendida a tiempo abre la puerta a que la venta acabe en otro negocio.",
      },
      {
        title: "Seguimiento inexistente",
        body: "Sin un sistema, el día a día se come los contactos y se escapan oportunidades reales.",
      },
    ],
    solutionLabel: "LA SOLUCIÓN",
    solutionTitle: "Por eso creé este servicio",
    solutionParagraphs: [
      "Mi objetivo es ayudar a negocios que reciben contactos de clientes, pero que no siempre pueden responder a tiempo, a recuperar esas oportunidades antes de que se pierdan.",
      "Lo hago implementando sistemas simples que detectan llamadas o consultas no atendidas y responden automáticamente para convertirlas en reservas o en conversaciones con el negocio.",
      "La idea es sencilla: si un cliente intentó contactar contigo, no deberías perder esa venta solo porque en ese momento estabas ocupado atendiendo el negocio.",
    ],
    foundersLabel: "FUNDADORES",
    foundersTitle: "Las personas detrás de ATOM",
    founders: [
      {
        name: "Zeki",
        role: "Co-founder",
        image: "/zeki.png",
        body: "Construye sistemas que convierten contactos perdidos en conversaciones reales para el negocio.",
      },
      {
        name: "Nate",
        role: "Co-founder",
        image: "/nate.png",
        body: "Se enfoca en crear procesos simples, útiles y fáciles de implantar para pequeñas empresas.",
      },
    ],
    ctaLabel: "NUESTRA MISIÓN",
    ctaTitle: "Que ningún cliente interesado se quede sin respuesta",
    ctaBody:
      "Diseñamos automatizaciones pensadas para negocios reales, con problemas reales y con necesidad de resultados rápidos.",
    ctaButton: "Ver precios",
    footer: "© 2026 ATOM. Todos los derechos reservados.",
  },
  en: {
    heroLabel: "WHO WE ARE",
    heroTitle: "We recover opportunities your business loses every day",
    heroBody:
      "We help restaurants and small businesses stop losing bookings, sales, and valuable conversations when they cannot reply in time.",
    heroStats: [
      { value: "24/7", label: "Automatic response" },
      { value: "1 contact", label: "1 recoverable opportunity" },
      { value: "0 excuses", label: "To lose a sale" },
    ],
    introLabel: "THE PROBLEM",
    introTitle: "What happens every day and almost nobody measures",
    introParagraphs: [
      "In many businesses, especially restaurants and small companies, something happens every day and almost nobody notices how much money it costs: calls that go unanswered, messages left without a reply, and customers who end up booking or buying somewhere else.",
      "Most owners are busy running the business, serving customers, coordinating the team, and solving day-to-day problems. Following up on calls or inquiries often becomes secondary, and that is exactly where real sales opportunities get lost.",
    ],
    painPoints: [
      {
        title: "Missed calls",
        body: "When you cannot answer the phone, many customers will not try a second time.",
      },
      {
        title: "Unanswered messages",
        body: "Every inquiry left hanging gives the sale a chance to end up with another business.",
      },
      {
        title: "No follow-up system",
        body: "Without a system, the day-to-day takes over and valuable leads quietly disappear.",
      },
    ],
    solutionLabel: "THE SOLUTION",
    solutionTitle: "That is why I created this service",
    solutionParagraphs: [
      "My goal is to help businesses that receive customer inquiries, but cannot always respond in time, recover those opportunities before they disappear.",
      "I do it by implementing simple systems that detect missed calls or unanswered inquiries and respond automatically to turn them into bookings or real conversations with the business.",
      "The idea is simple: if a customer tried to contact you, you should not lose that sale just because you were busy running the business at that moment.",
    ],
    foundersLabel: "FOUNDERS",
    foundersTitle: "The people behind ATOM",
    founders: [
      {
        name: "Zeki",
        role: "Co-founder",
        image: "/zeki.png",
        body: "Builds systems that turn missed contacts into real conversations for the business.",
      },
      {
        name: "Nate",
        role: "Co-founder",
        image: "/nate.png",
        body: "Focuses on creating simple, useful, and easy-to-implement processes for small businesses.",
      },
    ],
    ctaLabel: "OUR MISSION",
    ctaTitle: "No interested customer should go unanswered",
    ctaBody:
      "We design automations for real businesses, with real problems and a need for fast results.",
    ctaButton: "View pricing",
    footer: "© 2026 ATOM. All rights reserved.",
  },
} as const;

const copy = content[locale];
const pricingHref = locale === "en" ? "/en/pricing" : "/pricing";
---

<main class="features-page whoare-page">
  <section class="hero section">
    <div class="aurora aurora-main" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div class="container">
      <StudioPageNav active="whoare" locale={locale} />

      <div class="whoare-hero-grid">
        <div class="whoare-hero-copy">
          <p class="label">{copy.heroLabel}</p>
          <h2>{copy.heroTitle}</h2>
          <p class="body-lg limited">{copy.heroBody}</p>
        </div>

        <div class="whoare-hero-stats">
          {copy.heroStats.map((stat) => (
            <article class="hero-metric-card">
              <p class="value">{stat.value}</p>
              <p class="meta">{stat.label}</p>
            </article>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="aurora aurora-subtle" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-head about-head">
        <div>
          <p class="label">{copy.introLabel}</p>
          <h2>{copy.introTitle}</h2>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="whoare-story-grid">
        <div class="whoare-story-copy">
          {copy.introParagraphs.map((paragraph) => (
            <p class="body-lg">{paragraph}</p>
          ))}
        </div>

        <div class="whoare-pain-grid">
          {copy.painPoints.map((item) => (
            <article class="feature-card whoare-pain-card">
              <h3>{item.title}</h3>
              <p>{item.body}</p>
            </article>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="aurora aurora-main soft" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div class="container">
      <p class="label">{copy.solutionLabel}</p>
      <h2>{copy.solutionTitle}</h2>

      <div class="whoare-solution-panel">
        {copy.solutionParagraphs.map((paragraph) => (
          <p class="body-lg">{paragraph}</p>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="aurora aurora-subtle" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-head">
        <div>
          <p class="label">{copy.foundersLabel}</p>
          <h2>{copy.foundersTitle}</h2>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="whoare-founders-grid">
        {copy.founders.map((founder) => (
          <article class="feature-card founder-card">
            <img src={founder.image} alt={founder.name} class="founder-photo" />
            <h3>{founder.name}</h3>
            <p class="founder-role">{founder.role}</p>
            <p>{founder.body}</p>
          </article>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="aurora aurora-main soft" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-band">
        <div>
          <p class="label">{copy.ctaLabel}</p>
          <h2>{copy.ctaTitle}</h2>
          <p class="body-lg limited">{copy.ctaBody}</p>
        </div>

        <div class="cta-actions">
          <a class="plan-btn plan-btn-popular cta-link" href={pricingHref}>{copy.ctaButton}</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer class="footer">
    <div class="container footer-row">
      <div class="foot-brand">
        <img src="/ATOM.svg" alt="ATOM" class="foot-wordmark" />
      </div>
      <p>{copy.footer}</p>
    </div>
  </footer>
</main>
